# ─── napi-rs build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────
# `napi build` regenerates `index.js`, `index.d.ts`, and the per-target
# `.node` binaries (via macro expansion from `src/lib.rs`); `napi
# create-npm-dirs` regenerates `npm/<triple>/{README.md,package.json}`
# and `napi artifacts` stages `.node` files under `npm/<triple>/`. Source
# of truth is `src/lib.rs` and the root `package.json`. The npm tarball
# picks binaries up via each sub-package's `package.json#files`, not via
# git tracking, so tracked copies of generated files only risk drifting
# from the source.
#
# Exceptions that ARE tracked: `npm/<triple>/README.md` and
# `npm/<triple>/package.json` are checked in so that curated per-platform
# notes / publish config persist across `napi create-npm-dirs` runs. Run
# that command with caution — it overwrites these files from napi-rs
# templates.
index.js
index.d.ts
*.node

# ─── TypeScript ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.tsbuildinfo

# ─── OS / editor cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
